net.kyori.event

Interface PostOrders


  • public interface PostOrders
    The "post order" is a representation of the order, relative to other posts, that a given EventSubscriber should be posted events.

    Post orders are represented by Integers, and subscribers are ordered using the natural ordering of Java integers.

    Some "standard" post orders are expressed as constants on this class.
